Summary: A list of theme properties that can be used to customize the appearance of a Window node, including colors, fonts, icons, and styleboxes for its title bar and borders.

Theme Properties

* title_color (Color): The color of the title text. Default: Color(0.875, 0.875, 0.875, 1).
* title_outline_modulate (Color): The tint of the title's outline. Default: Color(0, 0, 0, 1).
* close_h_offset (int): The horizontal offset of the close button. Default: 18.
* close_v_offset (int): The vertical offset of the close button. Default: 24.
* resize_margin (int): The margin used for resizing the window. Default: 4.
* title_height (int): The height of the title bar. Default: 36.
* title_outline_size (int): The size of the title's outline. Default: 0.
* title_font (Font): The font used for the window's title.
* title_font_size (int): The font size for the window's title.
* close (Texture2D): The icon for the close button.
* close_pressed (Texture2D): The icon for the close button when it is pressed.
* embedded_border (StyleBox): The StyleBox for the border of embedded windows.
* embedded_unfocused_border (StyleBox): The StyleBox for the border of embedded windows when they are unfocused.
